&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 7 Clinical Specialist Physiotherapist &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elective Orthopaedics, Hospital of St Cross, Rugby&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full time – 37.5 hours/week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Therapy department at UHCW NHS Trust has an exciting opportunity for a highly skilled, motivated and enthusiastic Physiotherapist to join our existing clinical specialist in our Elective Orthopaedic Team at the Hospital of St Cross, Rugby.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work clinically within the elective orthopaedic service, providing highly specialist advice, assessments and treatments to this patient group. This requires both acute management of a variety of both routine and highly complex elective procedures and also sub-acute trauma cases. Therefore candidates will be expected to have significant experience, skills and knowledge within these areas as a band 6 or a current band 7. Knowledge of enhanced recovery pathways is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate should have excellent communication skills and also demonstrate strong leadership and organisational skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Therapy service at UHCW NHS Trust is an expanding, forward thinking and highly regarded service and this post offers excellent personal and professional development opportunities within an established, supportive team working closely with our Occupational Therapy colleagues. The Orthopaedic service at St Cross is an expanding service with ongoing investment in new operating facilities. They have close links with the Orthopaedic team at UHCW including the major trauma unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer an extended hours, 7 day service which the post holder would be required to be part of.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameKelly HollwayJob titleClinical Specialist PhysiotherapistEmail addresskelly.hollway@uhcw.nhs.ukTelephone number01788663054Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or email therapy.recruitment@uhcw.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
